name: PunFinder
0:
”Alexa, ask Pun Finder for puns on cheese.”
”Alexa, ask Pun Finder what's a pun for dog?”
”Alexa, tell Pun Finder to make some puns for cat.”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pun finder
des:
This skill quickly turns any word into a pun. Use it to create a joke, come up with a new handle for your social media account, or just for fun!

Also available on the web at https://puns.samueltaylor.org/
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
